Install a package called rpcbind and to install in linux following is the command 


"sudo apt-get install rpcbind" 

And after the installation or if you want to check if rpcbind is installed type rpcinfo, the command should display a table, if it doesnt then rpcbind should be installed or updated 

then do the folllowing

rpcgen os.x
cc server.c os_svc.c -o server -lnsl
cc client.c os_clnt.c -o client -lnsl

./server
./client <hostname> "enter the alphanumeric string with secret word C00l"

for example:

./client localhost heydudeC00L143


